<note resp="#resp1" n="0543019" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0543019">耆＋（經）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0543020" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="#resp1" target="#nkr_note_orig_0543020">應＋（而）【三】【宮】</note>
<note type="orig" place="foot text" n="0543021" resp="#resp1" target="#nkr_note_orig_0543021">（其）＋福【三】【宮】</note>
